type: software
title: cursor-kenji
abstract: >
  A curated toolkit of Cursor AI agent skills, slash commands, MCP server
  configurations, subagents, and project rules for full-stack development
  with React, Next.js, Supabase, Tailwind CSS, and TypeScript. Designed to
  make Cursor agents faster, more accurate, and production-ready out of the box.
